---
title: Indian Coconut Lentil & Veggie Dhal  with Herby Flatbreads
description: Dhal is the ultimate bowl of goodness – rich in protein, a good source of fibre and full of aromatic flavours. The coconut milk balances the spices to create a meal that's both delectable and nourishing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64d5c66b969a753cfcaf77c2-725f3def.jpeg
